  "texts": [
    "To determine studies eligible for inclusion in this work, we consider the following criteria:",
    "• It is written in English;",
    "• It is clearly focused on RL for environmental sustainability; • In the case of duplicate articles, the most recent version is included.",
    "Exclusion criteria.",
    "To further refine our search, we apply the following exclusion criteria: the study is an editorial, a conference review, or a book chapter."
  ]
}